{"tid":919573,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"花生敏感 馬浚偉慘變孖膶腸","createTime":"2018-11-28T06:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T11:10:22.000Z","uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"eb0c5301780ea16e90663014e55f5636d7401249","tid":919573,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T06:57:11.000Z","msg":"慘慘，唔小心食花生都唔知，咁就變左做孖膶腸<br />\n<br />\n今天凌晨，突然覺得嘴唇麻痹，找鏡子一照，發現嘴唇紅腫，口腔也腫起來，手掌也變得通紅&hellip;&hellip;本以為是偏頭痛藥的副作用，結果今早醒來，更見嚴重，於是馬上去醫院&hellip;&hellip;醫生診斷為嚴重的過敏反應，要馬上打針，因為可以很危險，最嚴重可引致窒息&hellip;&hellip;這是我有生以來第一次變成「孖潤腸咀」，我知自己對花生過敏，但沒想到會如此嚴重&hellip;&hellip;」他表示以後我會完全戒掉花生，並提醒有過敏症的朋友，要小心飲食，因為後果可以很嚴重很危險！他還打趣說：「不是只有梁朝偉才有孖潤腸」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2RkkuTw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2RkkuTw&d=7QB4h8mQ1QBJp1iJ1m8od7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a5d3696b\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2RkkuTw</a>"},{"pid":"339358d3c1a1c1de82cd6051ebaff3ea69f87670","tid":919573,"uid":86587,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條馬撚點樣我唔想知啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c32f92b2a151dfc9feb6849136756658cb2b89","tid":919573,"uid":37431,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"339358d3c1a1c1de82cd6051ebaff3ea69f87670","tid":919573,"uid":86587,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條馬撚點樣我唔想知啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"你又知佢馬撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebeccc717a546f9948577d51cf132f81def0e8ed","tid":919573,"uid":62822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:08:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"342f543ba2e2fcdaa4170fccc023b8938f